OL,7,FMs Sturgeon was SNP leader and
OL,8,FScottish first minister when the power-
OL,9,Fsharing deal was agreed in the
OL,10,Faftermath of the 2021 Holyrood
OL,11,Felection ` with Mr Ewing claiming she
OL,12,Fhad "brought the Greens into
OL,13,Fgovernment not having mentioned this
OL,14,Fto the electorate beforehand".
OL,16,FIn an interview with the Institute for
OL,17,FGovernment think tank, he said: "I
OL,18,Fwould say that Nicola gradually took
OL,19,Fthe party and the policies in a
OL,20,Fdirection that I thought was really
OL,21,Fnot going to work out."
