OL,3,CFergus Ewing: Sturgeon took SNP in
OL,4,Cdirection that was 'really not going
OL,5,Cto work'
OL,7,FMr Ewing, who served as the Scottish
OL,8,FGovernment's rural economy secretary
OL,9,Funder Ms Sturgeon, insisted they had
OL,10,F"parted on amicable terms" when he was
OL,11,F"dispatched" from her cabinet in 2021.
OL,13,FBut he went on to become a vocal
OL,14,Fcritic of the decision to bring the
OL,15,FScottish Greens into government with
OL,16,Fthe SNP.
