OL,3,CFergus Ewing: Sturgeon took SNP in
OL,4,Cdirection that was 'really not going
OL,5,Cto work'
OL,7,FMr Ewing, who has previously branded
OL,8,Fthe Greens "winebar revolutionaries",
OL,9,Frecalled: "I spoke out against it. I
OL,10,Fwas the only person in my group to do
OL,11,Fso. "
OL,13,FThe SNP MSP said he feared his party
OL,14,Fwould be "tarnished by association"
OL,15,Fand would be "damaged" by supporting
OL,16,Fpolicies backed by the Greens on
OL,17,Fissues such as gender recognition and
OL,18,Fthe deposit return scheme for drinks
OL,19,Fcans and bottles ` both areas where
OL,20,FScottish Government attempts at reform
OL,21,Ffailed.
